<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Página no encontrada - MiEcommerce</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.13.1/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .not-found-content {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            min-height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .not-found-content h1 {
            font-size: 6rem;
            color: #ff4757;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .not-found-content h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .not-found-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #747d8c;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .btn-home {
            background-color: #2f3542;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-home:hover {
            background-color: #57606f;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/organisms/header') %>
    
    <main class="not-found-content">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>¡Oops! Página no encontrada</h2>
        <p>Parece que el recurso que buscás no existe o ha sido movido.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">Volver al Inicio</a>
    </main>

    <%- include('./partials/organisms/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
